data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
FusionLeaf Studio is the management tool for FusionLeaf Stack, a preconfigured distribution of web components. Use the Start button below to quickly start all the default applications. The Advanced and Apache tabs can be used to control and monitor the services individually.
Components: Ngnix (Web Server), Apache (Web Server), PHP (FastCGI), Adminer (Database Management Tool), MySQL (Database), Memcached (Caching System)
Use the Edit menu above to edit the startup configurations, but don't replace any of the %VARIABLES%. The variables will be replaced when the Start button is clicked. You can view the running configurations through the View menu.
